sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Admin/User
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>mTLS
    participant Controller as DSC Controller<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    participant Manifests as Local Filesystem<br/>/opt/manifests
    participant Components as Component Deployments<br/>(Dashboard, KServe, etc.)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Creation

    User->>API: POST DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Bearer Token (User)
    API->>Webhook: POST /validate-datasciencecluster<br/>mTLS (API Server cert)
    Webhook->>API: GET existing resources<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    API-->>Webhook: Resource data
    Webhook-->>API: Validation response (allow/deny)
    API->>Webhook: POST /mutate-datasciencecluster<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>API: Mutated CR (defaults applied)
    API-->>User: CR created confirmation

    Note over Controller,API: Watch triggered
    Controller->>API: GET DataScienceCluster<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    API-->>Controller: DSC resource data

    Note over Controller,Components: Flow 2: Component Manifest Deployment

    Controller->>API: GET DSCInitialization<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    API-->>Controller: DSCI resource data
    Controller->>Manifests: Read component manifests<br/>Filesystem access
    Manifests-->>Controller: YAML manifest files

    loop For each enabled component
        Controller->>API: Apply manifests<br/>(Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps, etc.)<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
        API-->>Controller: Resource created/updated
    end

    Controller->>API: PATCH DataScienceCluster/status<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    API-->>Controller: Status updated

    Note over Prometheus,Components: Flow 3: Monitoring and Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics (8443/TCP)<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (Prometheus SA)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Operator metrics
    Prometheus->>Components: GET component metrics<br/>HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token
    Components-->>Prometheus: Component metrics

    Note over Controller,API: Flow 4: Service Mesh Integration (KServe)

    Controller->>API: POST ServiceMeshControlPlane<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    API-->>Controller: SMCP created
    Controller->>API: POST ServiceMeshMember<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    API-->>Controller: SMM created
    Controller->>API: POST AuthorizationPolicy<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    API-->>Controller: AuthZ policy created
